<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-07-17T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-07-17T16:00:00-05:00" n="181" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d181">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72119/681a</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of
                                        State</gloss> to the Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_SPA1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Stovall</hi></persName>)</head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-07-17T16:00:00-05:00">
                                        <hi rend="italic">July 17, 1917, 4 p.m.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>762. Please deliver the following cipher message to <persName corresp="#p_MJC1">McNally</persName>:<note n="1" xml:id="d181fn1">
                                    <persName corresp="#p_MJC1">James C. McNally</persName>, Vice
                                    Consul at Zürich.</note>
                            </p>
                            <p>Department informed from reliable source that present conference
                                between the Emperors of Germany and Austria-Hungary at Vienna is due
                                to strong desire of Emperor of Austria-Hungary for peace on best
                                terms obtainable, and that probably within one month propaganda will
                                be launched in the United States to prepare the people for offer of
                                inclusive peace from the enemy. Have you heard anything regarding
                                this? If so, report fully by telegraph.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_PFL1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>